      <title>交易规模扩大后，生物科技 IPO 股票在交易首日上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/biotech-ipo-shares-climb-in-trading-debuts-after-deals-upsized</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三家生物科技公司在各自的首次公开募股中出售的股票数量均超出计划，因此，它们的股价在首个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/biotech-ipo-shares-climb-in-trading-debuts-after-deals-upsized</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 17:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
