    <item>
      <title>罢工影响生产，波音面临被降级为垃圾飞机的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/boeing-at-risk-of-being-cut-to-junk-as-strike-hurts-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司面临失去投资级信用评级的风险，因为这家陷入困境的飞机制造商可能面临工人长期罢工的威胁，这将进一步扰乱生产和现金流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/boeing-at-risk-of-being-cut-to-junk-as-strike-hurts-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 16:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的加密货币交易员曾以“混蛋”形象示人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-13/trump-s-crypto-dealmaker-once-reveled-in-dirtbag-image-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Zeke Faux 揭秘了 Chase Herro 的故事，他是前总统唐纳德·特朗普推动的加密货币新冒险背后的推手。Faux 在“彭博未平仓合约”中表示，Herro 在业内鲜为人知，曾称自己为“互联网上的混蛋”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-13/trump-s-crypto-dealmaker-once-reveled-in-dirtbag-image-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 14:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德暗示欧洲央行可能在 10 月降息，但 12 月更有可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，如果经济遭遇重大挫折，欧洲央行愿意在 10 月份考虑降息——尽管下一轮全面信息要到下次会议上才能公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-officials-stick-with-call-for-gradual-cuts-in-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风暴弗朗辛过后，油价短暂反弹后回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在风暴弗朗辛过后，生产商开始恢复生产，油价随之下跌，但由于广泛市场的混乱和冒险情绪帮助缓解了此前超卖的原油市场，期货价格仍有望实现一个月以来的首次周度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市轮动重回押注美联储将“大手笔出手”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员重新燃起对美联储下周降息半个百分点的预期，刺激投资者转向最能从政策放松中受益的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:17:37 GMT</pubDate>
